## Getting Started
### Prerequisites:
Join our [Discord Server](https://discord.gg/YRdff5T) to get started and type this:
### Get yourself known:
You can type
```
-help
```
for a list of commands and
```
-info
```
for a detailed info about our [Discord Server](https://discord.gg/YRdff5T)
### Deployment:
I was deployed using [Heroku](https://www.heroku.com/#) which is connected to this repository.
